T02D2033:130a-1: rakta ya m'anta ka yantra autta ka /
T02D2033:130a-3: gshin rje gshed dmar po'i 'khor lo'i gsal byed //
T02D2033:130a-4: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2033:130a-6: nya gro dha'i lo ma la sogs pa la /
T02D2033:130a-7: dang po 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa zlum po //
T02D2033:130a-8: gnyis pa la rtsibs bcu gnyis pa /
T02D2033:130b-0: gsum pa @130b la rtsibs bcu drug pa /
T02D2033:130b-1: rtsibs brgyad pa'i phyogs su ya ma la sogs pa'i yi ge dgong /
T02D2033:130b-2: mtshams kyi 'dab ma la bsgrul bya'i ming gi yi ge dgod //
T02D2033:130b-3: rtsibs bcu drug pa'i rtsibs kyi bar gyi rtsibs brgyad la /
T02D2033:130b-4: de ltar bsgrub bya zur rnams su'o //
T02D2033:130b-5: 'khor lo dang po'i dbus kyi lte bar /
T02D2033:130b-8: rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i shar du r'a /
T02D2033:130b-12: rtsibs brgyad pa'i lho'i rtsibs la me /
T02D2033:130b-13: slar yang rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i 'dab ma lnga pa la ru //
T02D2033:130b-16: slar yang rtsibs brgyad kyi nub kyi 'dab ma la da /
T02D2033:130b-17: yang rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i rtsibs brgyad pa la ni /
T02D2033:130b-20: slar yang rtsibs brgyad pa'i byang gi rtsibs la kshe /
T02D2033:130b-21: yang rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i bcu gcig pa la tstsha /
T02D2033:130b-24: yam r'a dzas do me ya /
T02D2033:130b-25: ya med ru na yo da ya /
T02D2033:130b-26: ya da yo ni ra ya kshe ya /
T02D2033:130b-27: ya kshe ya tstsha ni r'a ma ya /
T02D2033:130b-28: zhes pa rtsa ba'i sngags so //
T02D2033:130b-29: yi ge bcu drug ni rtsibs bcu drug la'o //
T02D2033:130b-30: gcig ni gtso bo'i ste 'di ltar dbus su rab tu 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T02D2033:130b-31: ya ma r'a da sa dom ru na yo //
T02D2033:130b-32: de nas dbus kyi snying po'i rtsibs nas 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T02D2033:130b-34: de nas na'i mtha' can no //
T02D2033:130b-36: rtsibs bcu gnyis pa'i des pa'o //
T02D2033:130b-37: de nas rtsibs bcu drug pa'i dangs bsgrub bya'i mid
T02D2033:130b-38: gi bar bar gyi 'dab ma la sngags 'di rnams
T02D2033:130b-40: aom hr'i: shnri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D2033:130b-41: sdad pa rnam par dbye ba lad bus su gtso bo ya'o //
T02D2033:130b-43: dbang du sdud pa la r'a 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T02D2033:130b-48: stobs dang ldan par bya ba la do //
T02D2033:130b-51: chad pa btab pa la na /
T02D2033:130b-54: rab tu gdung ba la yo //
T02D2033:130b-55: dgra brlag par bya ba la ni /
T02D2033:130b-56: 'dir las kyi rang bzhin gyis yi ge dbus su
T02D2033:130b-57: gtso bor gyur pa de'i gnas su ya bri bar
T02D2033:131a-0: / gshin rje gshed kyi 'khor lo la des pa 'di dang po'i sangs rgyas @131a * //
T02D2033:131a-3: // /'di rnams kyi zhi ba la sogs pa'i las 'chad
T02D2033:131a-4: par 'gyur ba'i 'khor lo bri ba'i cho ga brjod
T02D2033:131a-5: de / de la zhi ba dang rgyas pa'i 'khor
T02D2033:131a-6: lo ni n+ya gro dha'i lo ma rlan dad ma
T02D2033:131a-8: 'bras s'a lu btags pa'i chu yis /
T02D2033:131a-10: rgyas pa la 'jag rgod dkar po la sogs pas bri'o //
T02D2033:131a-11: de bzhin du gsad pa dang bskrad pa la dur
T02D2033:131a-12: khrod kyi ras la dug dang khrag dang sol bas
T02D2033:131a-13: mi rus kyi smyu gus so //
T02D2033:131a-14: skrod pa la bya rog gi sgro rkang gis bri'o //
T02D2033:131a-15: dbang du bya ba dang dgug pa la gro ga
T02D2033:131a-16: la gur gum dang gi wang gser gyi thur mas
T02D2033:131a-17: so // dgug pa la tsandan dmar po seng ldeng gi smyu gus so //
T02D2033:131a-18: rengs pa dang rmongs pa ni mchod spyin gyi lo
T02D2033:131a-19: ma yongs su smin pa kha dog ser po la
T02D2033:131a-20: 'bras bu gsum gyi khu ba dang bsres pa'i ba
T02D2033:131a-22: ka ped kyi smyu gu dang mchod spyin gyi smyu gus rmongs par byed pa la'o//
T02D2033:131a-25: // /'khor lo de rnams kyi rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga bshad de /
T02D2033:131a-26: zhi ba dang rgyas pa'i 'khor lo bris la /
T02D2033:131a-27: 'khor lo la sogs pa skud pa dkar pos bcing bar bya /
T02D2033:131a-28: ji ltar 'khor lo mi mthong ba'i tshul lo //
T02D2033:131a-29: de bzhin las kyi bye brag gis skud pa dkar po dang /
T02D2033:131a-31: de nas zhi dang rgyas pa ni mar dang 'o
T02D2033:131a-32: ma dang sbrang gis bkang ba'i rdza phor kha sbyar
T02D2033:131a-33: du gzhag pa'o // gsang pa dang bskrad pa la thod pa khrag gis bkang bar gzhag par bya /
T02D2033:131a-34: dbang dang dgug pa la spra tshil gyis g-yogs la gyo mo kha sbyar du mes gdung bar bya'o //
T02D2033:131a-35: mnan pa dang rmongs pa la ba bla'i chus bkang ba'i so phag dbus su gzhag par bya'o //
T02D2033:131a-36: gnas gtsang zhing rlan dang bcas pa'i mandala gyi steng
T02D2033:131a-37: du zhi ba dang rgyas pa la gzhag par bya'o
T02D2033:131a-38: // gsad pa dang bskrang [*bskrad?] pa la dong gi
T02D2033:131a-39: nang du zho dang mar blugs la sba bar bya'o
T02D2033:131a-40: // // dgug pa dang dbang la thab kyi 'og tu'o //
T02D2033:131a-41: mnan pa dang rmongs pa ni sa skam por sba bar bya'o //
T02D2033:131a-42: dge ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyi 'bras bu 'di ni sngags pas nges par rig par bya'o //
T02D2033:131a-43: 'khor lo bris ba de rnams kyi phyi rol gyi 'khor lo'i nges pa gsungs te /
T02D2033:131a-44: de la zhi ba'i 'khor lo'i phyi rol tu zla
T02D2033:131b-0: ba'i @131b dkyil 'khor gyis bskor zhing re kh'a sa
T02D2033:131b-1: bskor bar bya'o // rgyas pa la glang po ches bskor bar bya ste /
T02D2033:131b-2: ji ltar glang po che'i lto bar 'khor lo chud pa'o //
T02D2033:131b-3: gsad pa la yi dvags kyi lus su'o //
T02D2033:131b-4: bskrad pa la rnga mo'i lto bar ro //
T02D2033:131b-5: dbang du bsdu ba la ri dgas kyi lto bar ro //
T02D2033:131b-6: dgug pa la rta'i lto bar ro //
T02D2033:131b-7: rmongs pa la ra'i lto ba'am lug gi lto bar ro //
T02D2033:131b-8: mnan pa rus spel gyi lto bar ro //
T02D2033:131b-10: phyi rol gzugs kyang de bzhin no //
T02D2033:131b-11: de nas gong du gsungs pa'i skud pas dkri bar bya'o //
T02D2033:131b-12: rig pa de rnams kyi dus su thun gyi nges pas gsungs te /
T02D2033:131b-13: thun dang po phyed g-yon pa chu'i dkyil 'khor la kha byang du bltas te zhi ba'i las sgrub /
T02D2033:131b-14: thun byed kyi gnyis pa la de bzhin du rgyas pa'i las la dbang ldan du kha bltas la'o //
T02D2033:131b-15: thun tshod gnyis pa'i thun phyed la g-yas pa rlung
T02D2033:131b-16: gi dkyil 'khor rgyu ba'i tshe kha shar du bltas
T02D2033:131b-18: thun tshod gnyis pa'i phyed kyi phyi ma la me ru bltas te bskrad pa'i las sgrub /
T02D2033:131b-19: thun tshod gsum pa'i phyed la g-yas pa me'i dkyil
T02D2033:131b-20: 'khor gyi dus su kha lho ru bltas te dbang
T02D2033:131b-21: gi las sgrub / thun tshod gsum pa'i phyed kyi
T02D2033:131b-22: phyi ma la bden bral du bltas te dgug pa'i
T02D2033:131b-23: gi las sgrub / las sgrub / thun tshod bzhi
T02D2033:131b-24: pa la g-yas pa sa'i dkyil 'khor 'byung ba'i dus
T02D2033:131b-25: su kha nub tu bltas te mnan pa'i las sgrub
T02D2033:131b-26: gi las sgrub / las sgrub / / thun tshod
T02D2033:131b-27: bzhi pa'i phyed la rlung du bltas te rmongs pa'i
T02D2033:131b-28: gi las sgrub / las sgrub / / las sgrub
T02D2033:131b-29: / dbang du bya ba dang dgug pa ni gro
T02D2033:131b-30: ga la gur gum dang gi wang la gser gyi
T02D2033:131b-31: gi las sgrub / las sgrub / / las sgrub
T02D2033:131b-32: / smyu gus bri / zhi ba dang rgyas pa
T02D2033:131b-33: la n+ya gro dha'i lo ma la d'ur bas 'bras
T02D2033:131b-35: gsad pa dang bskrad pa ni dur khrod kyi ras la sogs pa dag la mi'i rus pas so //
T02D2033:131b-36: mnan pa dang rmongs pa dag la so phag gi phyi ma 'am yung bas so //
T02D2033:131b-37: 'khor lo'i cho ga nye bar bsdus pa rdzogs so /
T02D2033:131b-39: // / panti ta rdo rje gdan pa ni ska lam ka'i zhal snga nas /
